Class CustomGallery

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.kskelm.baringo.model.gallery.CustomGallery

  • public class CustomGallery
extends java.lang.Object
    A user's custom gallery is specific tags they want to search on. It also represents a list of blocked tags that the user never, ever wants to see.
    Author:
    Kevin Kelm (triggur@gmail.com)
